msgid "不得吸食食應當學。"
msgstr "Not to slurp up food while eating should be trained."

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="sk52" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:556.1"
msgid "sekhiya 52"
msgstr "sekhiya 52"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:557.1"
msgid "不得全吞食應當學。"
msgstr "Not to eat swallowing (the food) whole should be trained."

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="sk53" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:558.1"
msgid "sekhiya 53"
msgstr "sekhiya 53"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:559.1"
msgid "不得落飯食應當學。"
msgstr "Not to drop food while eating should be trained."

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="sk54" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:560.1"
msgid "sekhiya 54"
msgstr "sekhiya 54"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:561.1"
msgid "不得振手食應當學。"
msgstr "Not to shake the hand while eating should be trained."

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="sk55" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:562.1"
msgid "sekhiya 55"
msgstr "sekhiya 55"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:563.1"
msgid "不得嫌心看比坐<span class=\"gaiji\">鉢<!--gaiji,缽,1[金*本],2&#x9262;,3--> </span>食應當學。"
msgstr "Not to look at and compare a sitting person’s bowl with dissatisfaction while eating should be trained."

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="sk56" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:564.1"
msgid "sekhiya 56"
msgstr "sekhiya 56"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:565.1"
msgid "端心視<span class=\"gaiji\">鉢<!--gaiji,缽,1[金*本],2&#x9262;,3--> </span>食應當學。"
msgstr "Observing the bowl with an upright mind while eating should be trained."

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="sk57" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:566.1"
msgid "sekhiya 57"
msgstr "sekhiya 57"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:567.1"
msgid "不病不得為己索食應當學。"
msgstr "Not to ask for food for oneself when not sick should be trained."

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="sk58" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:568.1"
msgid "sekhiya 58"
msgstr "sekhiya 58"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:569.1"
msgid "不得以飯覆羹更望得應當學。"
msgstr "Not to cover the soups with rice hoping to get more should be trained."

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="sk59" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:570.1"
msgid "sekhiya 59"
msgstr "sekhiya 59"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:571.1"
msgid "不得以膩手受飲器應當學。"
msgstr "Not to receive drinking utensils with a dirty hand should be trained."

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="sk60" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:572.1"
msgid "sekhiya 60"
msgstr "sekhiya 60"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:573.1"
msgid "不得以<span class=\"gaiji\">鉢<!--gaiji,缽,1[金*本],2&#x9262;,3--> </span>中殘食棄地應當學。"
msgstr "Not to throw food leftover in the bowl on the ground should be trained."

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="sk61" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:574.1"
msgid "sekhiya 61"
msgstr "sekhiya 61"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:575.1"
msgid "人坐比丘尼立不得為說法除病應當學。"
msgstr "Not to teach dhamma to a person who is sitting when the bhikkhunī is standing, unless they are sick, should be trained."

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="sk62" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:576.1"
msgid "sekhiya 62"
msgstr "sekhiya 62"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:577.1"
msgid "人臥比丘尼坐不得為說法除病應當學。"
msgstr "Not to teach dhamma to a person lying down when the bhikkhunī is sitting, unless they are sick, should be trained."

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="sk63" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:578.1"
msgid "sekhiya 63"
msgstr "sekhiya 63"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:579.1"
msgid "人在高床比丘尼卑床不得為說法除病應當學。"
msgstr "Not to teach dhamma to a person sitting on a high bed when the bhikkhunī is sitting on a low bed, unless they are sick, should be trained."

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="sk64" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:580.1"
msgid "sekhiya 64"
msgstr "sekhiya 64"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:581.1"
msgid "不得為著革屣人說法除病應當學。"
msgstr "Not to teach dhamma to a person wearing leather sandals, unless they are sick, should be trained."

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="sk65" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:582.1"
msgid "sekhiya 65"
msgstr "sekhiya 65"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:583.1"
msgid "不得為著屐人說法除病應當學。"
msgstr "Not to teach dhamma to a person wearing wooden sandals, unless they are sick, should be trained."

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="sk66" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:584.1"
msgid "sekhiya 66"
msgstr "sekhiya 66"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:585.1"
msgid "不得為覆頭人說法除病應當學。"
msgstr "Not to teach dhamma to a person with their head covered, unless they are sick, should be trained."

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="sk67" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:586.1"
msgid "sekhiya 67"
msgstr "sekhiya 67"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:587.1"
msgid "不得為纏頭人說法除病應當學。"
msgstr "Not to teach dhamma to a person with their head wrapped, unless they are sick, should be trained."

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="sk68" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:588.1"
msgid "sekhiya 68"
msgstr "sekhiya 68"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:589.1"
msgid "不得為抱膝蹲人說法除病應當學。"
msgstr "Not to teach dhamma to a person who sits clasping their knees, unless they are sick, should be trained."

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="sk69" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:590.1"
msgid "sekhiya 69"
msgstr "sekhiya 69"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:591.1"
msgid "不得為翹<span class=\"gaiji\">脚<!--gaiji,腳,1[腳-谷+去],2&#x811A;,3--> </span>人說法除病應當學。"
msgstr "Not to teach dhamma to a person with their feet lifted up, unless they are sick, should be trained."

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="sk70" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:592.1"
msgid "sekhiya 70"
msgstr "sekhiya 70"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:593.1"
msgid "不得為持刀人說法除病應當學。"
msgstr "Not to teach dhamma to a person holding a knife, unless they are sick, should be trained."

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="sk71" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:594.1"
msgid "sekhiya 71"
msgstr "sekhiya 71"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:595.1"
msgid "不得為持弓箭人說法除病應當學。"
msgstr "Not to teach dhamma to a person holding bow and arrow, unless they are sick, should be trained."

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="sk72" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:596.1"
msgid "sekhiya 72"
msgstr "sekhiya 72"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:597.1"
msgid "不得為持杖人說法除病應當學。"
msgstr "Not to teach dhamma to a person holding a staff, unless they are sick, should be trained."

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="sk73" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:598.1"
msgid "sekhiya 73"
msgstr "sekhiya 73"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:599.1"
msgid "不得為持蓋人說法除病應當學。"
msgstr "Not to teach dhamma to a person holding an umbrella, unless they are sick, should be trained."

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="sk74" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:600.1"
msgid "sekhiya 74"
msgstr "sekhiya 74"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:601.1"
msgid "在後不為在前人說法除病應當學。"
msgstr "Not to teach dhamma to a person in front when one is behind, unless they are sick, should be trained."

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="sk75" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:602.1"
msgid "sekhiya 75"
msgstr "sekhiya 75"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:603.1"
msgid "不得為騎乘人說法除病應當學。"
msgstr "Not to teach dhamma to a person riding in a vehicle, unless they are sick, should be trained."

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="sk76" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:604.1"
msgid "sekhiya 76"
msgstr "sekhiya 76"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:605.1"
msgid "在道外不為道中人說法除病應當學。"
msgstr "Not to teach dhamma to a person on the path when one is off the path, unless they are sick, should be trained."

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="sk77" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:606.1"
msgid "sekhiya 77"
msgstr "sekhiya 77"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:607.1"
msgid "不得立大小便除病應當學<span class=\"t-counter\">(七十七事竟)</span>。"
msgstr "Not to defecate or urinate while standing, unless one is sick, should be trained. <span class=\"t-counter\">(End of 77 rules.)</span>"

#. </p><hr><p><a class="sc" id="40"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:608.1"
msgid "諸阿梨耶。已說眾學法。今問諸阿梨耶。是中清淨不。第二第三亦如是問。諸阿梨耶。是中清淨默然故。是事如是持。"
msgstr "Venerables, the many training rules have been recited. Now I ask the venerables: ‘Are you pure herein?’ A second and a third time, I ask this. The venerables are pure herein, therefore you are silent. This matter is remembered thus."

#. </p><h2>
#. <span class="add"><a id="as" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:609.1"
msgid "7 adhikaraṇasamathas"
msgstr "7 adhikaraṇasamathas"

#. </a></span>
#. </h2><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:610.1"
msgid "諸阿梨耶。是七滅諍法。半月半月波羅提木叉中說。"
msgstr "Venerables, these seven rules for settling disputes are recited every half-month in the pātimokkha."

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="as1" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:611.1"
msgid "adhikaraṇasamatha 1"
msgstr "adhikaraṇasamatha 1"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:612.1"
msgid "若隨事隨順人。應與現前毘尼人與。現前毘尼。"
msgstr "People should be dealt with according to the situation. To a person who should be given a removal in the presence, give a removal in the presence."

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="as2" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:613.1"
msgid "adhikaraṇasamatha 2"
msgstr "adhikaraṇasamatha 2"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:614.1"
msgid "應與憶念毘尼人。與憶念毘尼。"
msgstr "To a person who should given a removal through memory, give a removal through memory."

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="as3" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:615.1"
msgid "adhikaraṇasamatha 3"
msgstr "adhikaraṇasamatha 3"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:616.1"
msgid "應與不癡毘尼人。與不癡毘尼。"
msgstr "To a person who should be given a removal through non-confusion, give a removal through non-confusion."

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="as4" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:617.1"
msgid "adhikaraṇasamatha 4"
msgstr "adhikaraṇasamatha 4"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:618.1"
msgid "應與自言治人。與自言治。"
msgstr "Deal with a person who should be dealt with according to what they’ve admitted, according to what they’ve admitted."

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="as5" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:619.1"
msgid "adhikaraṇasamatha 5"
msgstr "adhikaraṇasamatha 5"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:620.1"
msgid "應與<span class=\"gaiji\">覔<!--gaiji,覓,1[不/見],2&#x8994;,3--> </span>罪相人。與覓罪相。"
msgstr "To a person who should be given a characteristic-of-seeking-offenses, give a characteristic-of-seeking-offenses."

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="as6" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:621.1"
msgid "adhikaraṇasamatha 6"
msgstr "adhikaraṇasamatha 6"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:622.1"
msgid "應與多處覓人與多處覓。"
msgstr "Deal with a person who should be dealt with by asking in many places, by asking in many places."

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="as7" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:623.1"
msgid "adhikaraṇasamatha 7"
msgstr "adhikaraṇasamatha 7"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:624.1"
msgid "應與如草布地比尼人。與如草布地比尼。"
msgstr "To a person who should be given a removal like grass spread on the ground, give a removal like grass spread on the ground."

#. </p><hr><p><a class="sc" id="41"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:625.1"
msgid "諸阿梨耶。已說七滅諍法。今問諸阿梨耶。是中清淨不。第二第三亦如是問。諸阿梨耶。是中清淨默然故。是事如是持。"
msgstr "Venerables, the seven rules for settling disputes have been recited. Now I ask the venerables: ‘Are you pure herein?’ A second and a third time, I ask this. The venerables are pure herein, therefore you are silent. This matter is remembered thus. "

#. </p><h2>
#. <span class="add"><a id="conc" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:626.1"
msgid "Conclusion"
msgstr "Conclusion"

#. </a></span>
#. </h2><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:627.1"
msgid "諸阿梨耶。已說波羅提木叉序。"
msgstr "Venerables, the introduction to the pātimokkha has been recited."

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:628.1"
msgid "已說八波羅夷法。"
msgstr "The eight pārājika rules have been recited."

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:629.1"
msgid "已說十九僧伽婆尸沙法。"
msgstr "The 19 saṅghādisesa rules have been recited."

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:630.1"
msgid "已說三十尼薩耆波夜提法。"
msgstr "The 30 nissaggiya pācittiya rules have been recited."

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:631.1"
msgid "已說百四十一波夜提法。"
msgstr "The 141 pācittiya rules have been recited."

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:632.1"
msgid "已說八波羅提提舍尼法。"
msgstr "The eight pātidesanīya rules have been recited."

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:633.1"
msgid "已說眾學法。"
msgstr "The many training rules have been recited."

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:634.1"
msgid "已說七滅諍法。"
msgstr "The seven rules for settling disputes have been recited."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="42"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:635.1"
msgid "是事入佛經中。半月半月波羅提木叉中說。及餘隨道法。諸阿梨耶。一心歡喜不諍。一學一道如水乳合。安樂行應當學。"
msgstr "In these matters, which are included in the Buddha’s suttas, and are recited every half-month in the pātimokkha, as well as in the remaining rules that accord with the path, the venerables should train single-mindedly, happily, without quarreling, with the same training and the same path, mixing like water and milk, living peacefully and happily."

#. </p><h2>
#. <span class="add"><a id="conc-verses" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:636.1"
msgid "Concluding verses"
msgstr "Concluding verses"

#. </a></span>
#. </h2><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:637.1"
msgid "佛告比丘尼毘婆尸佛如來應供正遍知為寂靜僧。最初說波羅提木叉。"
msgstr "The Buddha told the bhikkhunīs: Vipassī Buddha, the Tathāgata, worthy of offerings, the perfectly enlightened one, first spoke this pātimokkha to his quiet sangha:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:638.1"
msgid "忍辱第一道　　涅槃佛稱最"
msgstr "Patience is the best path, Nibbāna is praised most by the Buddhas,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:638.2"
msgid "出家惱他人　　不名為沙門"
msgstr "One gone forth who disturbs others can’t be called a samaṇa."

#. </p></blockquote><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:639.1"
msgid "尸棄佛如來應供正遍知為寂靜僧。最初說波羅提木叉。"
msgstr "Sikhī Buddha, the Tathāgata, worthy of offerings, the perfectly enlightened one, first spoke this pātimokkha to his quiet sangha:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:640.1"
msgid "譬如明眼人　　能避嶮惡道"
msgstr "Just as a person with clear eyes can avoid the dangerous evil path."

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:640.2"
msgid "世有聰明人　　能遠離諸惡"
msgstr "There are wise people in the world who can dwell far away from all evil."

#. </p></blockquote><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:641.1"
msgid "毘葉婆佛如來應供正遍知。為寂靜僧最初說波羅提木叉。"
msgstr "Vessabhū Buddha, the Tathāgata, worthy of offerings, the perfectly enlightened one, first spoke this pātimokkha to his quiet sangha:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:642.1"
msgid "不惱不說過　　如戒所說行"
msgstr "Without disturbing, without transgressing in speech, practising according to the laid-down precepts,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:642.2"
msgid "飯食知節量　　常樂在閑處"
msgstr "Knowing the right measure of food, always living happily in seclusion,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:642.3"
msgid "心淨樂精進　　是名諸佛教"
msgstr "Devoted to progress with a clear and happy mind, this is called the teaching of the Buddhas."

#. </p></blockquote><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:643.1"
msgid "拘留孫佛如來應供正遍知。為寂靜僧最初說波羅提木叉。"
msgstr "Kakusandha Buddha, the Tathāgata, worthy of offerings, the perfectly enlightened one, first spoke this pātimokkha to his quiet sangha:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p><a class="sc" id="43"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:644.1"
msgid "譬如蜂採華　　不壞色與香"
msgstr "Just as bees when they collect from flowers, do not damage their color or scent,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:644.2"
msgid "但取其味法　　比丘入聚落"
msgstr "Just taking their flavor they depart; A bhikkhu entering a village"

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:644.3"
msgid "不破壞他事　　不觀作不作"
msgstr "Should not damage the affairs of others, and not observe what is or isn’t being done."

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:644.4"
msgid "但自觀身行　　諦視善不善"
msgstr "He should just contemplate his own bodily conduct, and carefully observe good and bad."

#. </p></blockquote><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:645.1"
msgid "拘那含牟尼佛如來應供正遍知為寂靜僧最初說波羅提木叉。"
msgstr "Koṇāgamana Buddha, the Tathāgata, worthy of offerings, the perfectly enlightened one, first spoke this pātimokkha to his quiet sangha:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:646.1"
msgid "欲得好心莫放逸　　聖人善法當勤學"
msgstr "Desiring to obtain a good mind, don’t be negligent, a noble one in the good dhamma should strive in the training."

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:646.2"
msgid "若有智寂一心人　　乃能無復憂愁患"
msgstr "Someone with wisdom, and a quiet, one-pointed mind, need never again grieve and suffer."

#. </p></blockquote><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:647.1"
msgid "迦葉佛如來應供正遍知。為寂靜僧最初說波羅提木叉。"
msgstr "Kassapa Buddha, the Tathāgata, worthy of offerings, the perfectly enlightened one, first spoke this pātimokkha to his quiet sangha:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:648.1"
msgid "一切惡莫作　　當具足善法"
msgstr "Not doing all evil, fulfilling all good states,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:648.2"
msgid "自淨其志意　　是則諸佛教"
msgstr "Purifying one’s will and mind, this is the teaching of the Buddhas."

#. </p></blockquote><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:649.1"
msgid "釋迦牟尼佛如來應供正遍知。為寂靜僧最初說波羅提木叉。"
msgstr "Sakyamuni Buddha, the Tathāgata, worthy of offerings, the perfectly enlightened one, first spoke this pātimokkha to his quiet sangha:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p><a class="sc" id="44"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:650.1"
msgid "護身為善哉　　能護口亦善"
msgstr "Protecting the body is good, protecting the speech is also good,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:650.2"
msgid "護意為善哉　　護一切亦善"
msgstr "Protecting the mind is good, protecting everything is good."

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:650.3"
msgid "比丘護一切　　便得離眾苦"
msgstr "A bhikkhu who protects everything, will be free from many sufferings."

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:650.4"
msgid "比丘守口意　　身不犯眾惡"
msgstr "A bhikkhu who guards the speech, mind, and body, does not commit many evils."

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:650.5"
msgid "是三業道淨　　得聖所得道"
msgstr "When these three courses of action are pure, one will attain path attained by the noble ones. "

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:650.6"
msgid "若人撾罵不還報　　於嫌恨人心不恨"
msgstr "Not retaliating when people beat and scold, with a mind without hate towards hostile people,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:650.7"
msgid "於瞋人中心常淨　　見人為惡自不作"
msgstr "With a mind ever pure among hateful people, on seeing others doing evil not doing it oneself."

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:650.8"
msgid "七佛為世尊　　能救護世間"
msgstr "The seven Buddhas honored by the world, capable of saving and protecting the world, "

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:650.9"
msgid "是佛說戒經　　我已廣說竟"
msgstr "These Buddhas spoke this precepts sutta, which I have now finished explaining in detail."

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:650.10"
msgid "諸佛及弟子　　恭敬是戒經"
msgstr "The Buddhas and their disciples venerated this precepts sutta."

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:650.11"
msgid "恭敬戒經已　　各各相恭敬"
msgstr "Having venerated this precepts sutta, they venerated each other,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:650.12"
msgid "慚愧得具足　　能得無為道"
msgstr "And having fully developed conscience and prudence, they could attain the path of nibbāna."

#. </p></blockquote><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:651.1"
msgid "已說波羅提木叉竟僧一心得布薩。"
msgstr "The pātimokkha has been recited. The sangha has single-mindedly performed the uposatha.”"

#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "lzh-mg-bi-pm:652.1"
msgid "摩訶僧祇比丘尼戒本"
msgstr "Text of the Mahāsaṅghika Bhikkhunī precepts."



